title: Tumi Alpha Bravo Hickory Grissom Travel Satchel 222358 - Overview
description:
Tumi Alpha Bravo Hickory Grissom Travel Satchel - 222358 - HICKORY
http://www.abt.com/product/92099/Tumi-222358HICKORY.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=0222358HK2_20160310

Crafted from our ultra-durable ballistic nylon this sturdy and equally stylish Travel Satchel is equipped with a multitude of smart interior and exterior organizational pockets. Carry it by top handle or on your shoulder. Its the perfect gym bag carry-on or work week commuter.
Features:
• Primary Material: Ballistic Nylon 
• Interior Features:
o 2 zip pockets
o Key leash
• Exterior Features:
o Adjustable/removable shoulder strap
o Webbing top carry handles with leather accent
o Zip entry to main compartments
o Add-a-Bag sleeve
o Front U-zip pocket
o Back zipped pocket
o Luggage tag
